name: Yakima County Health District COVID Vaccination Site
info: *** PFIZER VACCINATIONS!!!!***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA DOSIS PFIZER!!! The vaccination clinic will take place at the Toppenish Post Office Park during the Toppenish Pancake Breakfast and Parade. Masks are required. Please wear clothing which allows access to your shoulder. Vaccinations at this site are reserved for people who live and/or work in Washington State. All individuals 12 and over are eligible to get vaccinated. Those under 18 must be accompanied by a parent/guardian or must get parental consent via video/phone call or paper format. La clínica de vacunación se ubicará en el parque del Toppenish Post Office. Se requieren máscaras. Por favor, use ropa que permita acceso a su brazo. special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
